ied anytime the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource.Select%2A> method is executed to retrieve data. In this example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource.FilterExpression%2A> contains a placeholder for a filter parameter, which is contained in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource.FilterParameters%2A> collection. In the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSource.Filtering> event, the filter parameter is displayed in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label> control.  \\n  \\n [!code-cs[System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSourceFiltering#1](~/add/codesnippet/csharp/p-system.web.ui.webcontr_491_1.aspx)]\\n [!code-vb[System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSourceFiltering#1](~/add/codesnippet/visualbasic/p-system.web.ui.webcontr_491_1.aspx)]\"\n  syntax:\n    content: public System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary ParameterValues { get; }\n    return:\n      type: System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary\n      description: An <xref href=\"System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary\"></xref> of <xref href=\"System.Web.UI.WebControls.Parameter\"></xref> objects.\n  overload: System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSourceFilteringEventArgs.ParameterValues*\n  exceptions: []\n  platform:\n  - net462\nreferences:\n- uid: System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs\n  isExternal: false\n  name: System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs\n- uid: System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSourceFilteringEventArgs.#ctor(System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary)\n  parent: System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSourceFilteringEventArgs\n  isExternal: false\n  name: SqlDataSourceFilteringEventArgs(IOrderedDictionary)\n  nameWithType: SqlDataSourceFilteringEventArgs.SqlDataSourceFilteringEventArgs(IOrderedDictionary)\n  fullName: System.Web.UI.WebControls.SqlDataSourceFilteringEventArgs.SqlDataSourceFilteringEventArgs(IOrderedDictionary)\n- uid: System.Collections.Specialized.IOrderedDictionary\n  parent: System.Collections.Specialized\n  isExternal: f